# NOTE: Slydee/Secrets.swift is intentionally TRACKED so Xcode Cloud / fresh
# clones can build. The Gemini key ships in the client binary anyway (it is
# extractable) — it MUST be restricted in Google AI Studio (API/app limits +
# quota) and moved behind a server proxy before public scale.

